prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style sloth wearing a party hat, hilariously attempting to blow out a single, very determined candle on a tiny cupcake, but the sloth is so slow that the candle has melted into a colorful wax puddle around the base. The sloth has a comically exasperated but endearing expression. In the center, below the sloth, the words "happy belated... oh wait, is it today? happy birthday" are written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is a flat 2D watercolor painting with soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture background, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the figures.
